[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolled by care team or auto-enrolled per    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    institutional policy]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cohort assignment (post-discharge, multi-condition,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      transitions-of-care, ACO-attributed, etc.)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to coordination          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      assistant interaction                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Information-sharing consent collected separately     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and revocable per category (PCP sharing, specialist  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      sharing, family-member sharing, employer sharing,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      community-resource sharing)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations enforced where     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      applicable                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-resource information surfaced                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; cohort assignment;      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    initialization of longitudinal store and               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    care-coordination plan]                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE + COORDINATION PLAN ────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-coordinator longitudinal store]                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions and care plans (consent-gated)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current medications (consent-gated)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team of record                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active referrals with status                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active prior auths with status                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled appointments across providers              │
