[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture per sharing category                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-coordination plan as structured state]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Transition-of-care protocol (where applicable)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pending coordination tasks with timelines and        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ownership                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Escalation thresholds                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cohort-specific protocols                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
