[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry per protocol]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-discharge day-N check-ins                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral status touch-points                         │
