[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous risk screening]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute clinical concern (chest pain, severe dyspnea,  │
